CREATE FUNCTION [dbo].[FN_CalculateDepreciationNew] (@ProductId nvarchar(20),@DepCalMethod nvarchar(100),@DateFrom Date,@Dateto Date,@AddOne int)
RETURNS numeric(16,2) 

AS BEGIN

--select dbo.FN_CalculateDepreciation(CodeNo,DepMethod,'2021-01-01') as OBDepAmount,
--(dbo.FN_CalculateDepreciation(CodeNo,DepMethod,'2021-12-31')-dbo.FN_CalculateDepreciation(CodeNo,DepMethod,'2021-01-01')) AS DepThisPeriod,
--Purchasedate , DepRate , TotalPrice ,*  
--from FixedAssetRegisterDetails
--where valid = 1 and Purchasedate between '2021-01-01' and '2021-12-31'


--DECLARE @Balance numeric(16,2); 

DECLARE @Balance numeric(16,2); 
DECLARE @CalDep numeric(16,2); 
DECLARE @DepRate numeric(16,2); 
DECLARE @CalTotalDep numeric(16,2); 
DECLARE @SalesValue numeric(16,2); 
DECLARE @NoofYear int=0;

DECLARE @NODSale int=0;

DECLARE	@Counter int= 1 ;

DECLARE @CurrentDate as Date;


SET @CurrentDate=@DateFrom

SET @NODSale=0;
SET @DepRate=0;
SET @CalDep = 0;
SET @SalesValue=0;
SET @Balance = 0;
SET @CalTotalDep=0;

SET @CalTotalDep = 0

IF @DepCalMethod = 'Diminishing Balance'					
	BEGIN
	--SET @NoofYear = (select Year(@Dateto) - Year(Purchasedate)  AS NoofYear from FixedAssetRegisterDetails where CodeNo = @ProductId and Valid = 1 AND DepMethod = 'Diminishing Balance' AND Purchasedate < @Dateto );
	
	SET @NoofYear = (select DATEDIFF(d,InvoiceDate,@Dateto)  AS NoofYear from FixedAssetRegisterDetails where AssetMainCode = @ProductId and Valid = 1 AND DeprecationMethod = 'Diminishing Balance' AND InvoiceDate <= @Dateto );
	
	IF @NoofYear IS NULL
		SET @NoofYear =0			
	ELSE 
		if @AddOne=1
			SET @NoofYear =@NoofYear+1		
		else
			SET @NoofYear =@NoofYear		
		
	
	--SET @SalesValue = [dbo].[FN_CalculateSalesValue] (@ProductId,@CurrentDate)
	
	SET @NODSale=(select DATEDIFF(d,Max(SalesDate),@Dateto)  AS NODSale from FixedAssetSales where AssetCode = @ProductId and Valid = 1 AND SalesDate <= @Dateto );
	
	IF @NODSale IS NULL
		SET @NODSale =0	
		
	SET @SalesValue = [dbo].[FN_CalculateSalesValue] (@ProductId,@Dateto)
	
	--SET @Balance = (select (ISNULL(TotalPrice,0)-ISNULL(opDepAmt,0)-ISNUll(carringAmt,0)) AS Balance from FixedAssetRegisterDetails where CodeNo = @ProductId and Valid = 1 AND DepMethod = 'Diminishing Balance');
	SET @Balance = (select (ISNULL(UnitPrice ,0)-ISNULL(opDepAmt,0)-ISNUll(carringAmt,0)) AS Balance from FixedAssetRegisterDetails where AssetMainCode  = @ProductId and Valid = 1 AND DeprecationMethod = 'Diminishing Balance');
	
	--SET @DepRate = (select DepRate from FixedAssetRegisterDetails where CodeNo = @ProductId and Valid = 1 AND DepMethod = 'Diminishing Balance');
	
	SET @DepRate = (select Rate from FixedAssetRegisterDetails where AssetMainCode = @ProductId and Valid = 1 AND DeprecationMethod = 'Diminishing Balance');
	
	--WHILE @Counter< = @NoofYear
	--	BEGIN
	--		--SET @CalDep = (SELECT  round((@Balance * 0.01 * (DepRate/365)),0) as depcal  from FixedAssetRegisterDetails where CodeNo = @ProductId and Valid = 1 AND DepMethod = 'Diminishing Balance' ) ;
			
	--		SET @CalDep = round(@Balance * 0.01 * (@DepRate/365),3)
	--		SET @Balance = round(@Balance,3)-round(@CalDep,3)-@SalesValue
	--		SET @CalTotalDep=round(@CalTotalDep,3)+round(@CalDep,3)
	--		SET @Counter= @Counter + 1
	--		SET @CurrentDate= DateADD(D,1,@CurrentDate)
	--		SET @SalesValue = [dbo].[FN_CalculateSalesValue] (@ProductId,@CurrentDate)
	--	END
		--set @CalTotalDep = (select CASE WHEN @CalTotalDep <0 then 0 else @CalTotalDep end)
		
		SET @CalTotalDep = [dbo].[fnc_FA_CalBalanceDimilisingAmount] (@Balance,@NoofYear,@DepRate)-[dbo].[fnc_FA_CalBalanceDimilisingAmount] (@SalesValue,@NODSale,@DepRate)
		
		RETURN @CalTotalDep
		
	END

IF @DepCalMethod = 'Straight Line'
	BEGIN
		SET @SalesValue = (SELECT SUM(SalesAmount) from FixedAssetSales where AssetCode = @ProductId and Valid = 1  AND Salesdate <= @dateTo);
		SET @CalTotalDep = 	(SELECT  round(((isnull(UnitPrice,0)-isnull(@SalesValue,0)-ISNULL(CarringAmt,0)-ISNULL(OPDepAmt,0)) * 0.01 * (Rate/365) * ((DATEDIFF(d,InvoiceDate,@Dateto)))),0) as depcal
						from FixedAssetRegisterDetails 
						where AssetMainCode  = @ProductId and Valid = 1 
						AND DeprecationMethod  = 'Straight Line' AND InvoiceDate <= @dateTo)
						
	END
--	set @CalTotalDep = (select CASE WHEN @CalTotalDep <0 then 0 else @CalTotalDep end)
	RETURN @CalTotalDep
	
END

GO
/****** Object:  UserDefinedFunction [dbo].[FN_CalculateSalesValue]    Script Date: 3/12/2026 6:25:13 AM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE FUNCTION [dbo].[FN_CalculateSalesValue] (@ProductId nvarchar(20),@GetDate Date)
RETURNS numeric(16,2) 

AS BEGIN

DECLARE @SalesValue numeric(16,2);
SET @SalesValue=0;
	SET @SalesValue = (select isnull(b.SalesAmount,0) as SalesAmount
						from
						(Select CodeNo from FixedAssetRegister) a left join
						(Select AssetCode,SUM(SalesAmount) as SalesAmount from FixedAssetSales where Valid=1 
						and SalesDate<=@GetDate group by AssetCode) b on a.CodeNo=b.AssetCode
						where a.CodeNo=@ProductId
						);
	RETURN @SalesValue;
	
END
GO
/****** Object:  UserDefinedFunction [dbo].[fn_IndoorDueAmount]    Script Date: 3/12/2026 6:25:13 AM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO

CREATE FUNCTION [dbo].[fn_IndoorDueAmount]
(
	@BranchId INT, 
	@PatientId VARCHAR(50)
)
RETURNS MONEY
AS
BEGIN 
	/*Condition for IsInclude Pharmacy bill*/
	DECLARE @IncludePharmacy INT, @IsIncludePharmacy INT;
	SELECT @IsIncludePharmacy = PharmacyInclude FROM tbl_ComInfo
	IF @IsIncludePharmacy = 1 BEGIN SET @IncludePharmacy = 1 END ELSE BEGIN SET @IncludePharmacy = 5 END
	RETURN	
	(
		SELECT ISNULL(SUM(Due), 0) AS Due FROM
		(
			SELECT 1 AS SlNo, SUM(a.TotalAmount-a.Less-a.Collection) AS Due
			FROM PatientLedger a
			WHERE a.BranchId = @BranchId AND Valid = 1 AND a.PatientId = @PatientId
			HAVING SUM(a.TotalAmount-a.Less-a.Collection) > 0
			UNION
			SELECT 2 AS SlNo, ISNULL(SUM(a.Sales-a.Less-a.Collection-a.ReturnDue-a.AdjustAmt), 0) AS Due
			FROM SalesLedger a
			WHERE a.BranchId = @BranchId AND a.Valid = 1 AND a.PatientId = @PatientId
			HAVING ISNULL(SUM(a.Sales-a.Less-a.Collection-a.ReturnDue-a.AdjustAmt), 0) > 0
			UNION
			SELECT 3 AS SlNo, ISNULL(SUM(a.Sales-a.LessAmt-a.Collection-a.DueLess-a.DueColl-a.ReturnAmt-a.AdjustAmt), 0) AS Due
			FROM PharSalesLedger a
			WHERE a.BranchId = @BranchId AND a.Valid = @IncludePharmacy AND a.PatientId = @PatientId
			HAVING ISNULL(SUM(a.Sales-a.LessAmt-a.Collection-a.DueLess-a.DueColl-a.ReturnAmt-a.AdjustAmt), 0) > 0
		) aa
	);
END
GO
